title: The Black Book (1949) Reign of Terror

sources.title: The Black Book (1949) Reign of Terror
sources.description:
Stars: Robert Cummings, Richard Basehart, Richard Hart
Director: Anthony Mann

Robespierrre, a powerful figure in the French revolution, is desperately looking for his black book, a death list of those marked for the guillotine. Cinematography by FILM NOIR lensman John Alton!
